                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.R.1.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 12</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian"
                        notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00"
                        >undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>Replace the wording of paragraph 1 of Article 12 of the draft Peace Treaty with
                    Italy by the following text: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Italy hereby cedes to Greece in full sovereignty the Dodecanese Islands.
                            These Islands shall be and shall remain <hi rend="italic"
                                >completely</hi> demilitarised.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
